  .email-card {
    max-width: 90%;
  }
}
```

The key points:

- Use a wrapper div to center the card with flexbox
- Set max-width on the card itself 
- Margin auto for horizontal centering
- Media query to adjust max-width on smaller screens

This will keep the card centered and responsive.

