    </div>
  ))}
</div>
```

Replace the line `<span> {imageName}</span>` with `<span> Clear and Face</span>`. This will display "Clear and Face" instead of the image name for all the images.

```jsx
<div style={{ display: 'flex', flexWrap: 'wrap', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
