In this updated code, I've made the following changes:

1. Wrapped the URL `https://jobxdubai.com/aiheadshot` with a `Link` component from Material-UI.
2. Added the `target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"` attributes to the `Link` component to open the URL in a new tab and prevent security vulnerabilities.
3. Styled the `Link` component with a blue color and removed the underline using `textDecoration: 'none'`.

With these changes, the URL will now be clickable and open in a new tab, and it will also have a distinct blue color to make it stand out from the rest of the text.

