  // ...

  return (
    // ...
  );
}

export default Headshot;
```

Make sure to add the import statement `import AWS from 'aws-sdk';` at the top of your component file, along with the other import statements.

With the AWS SDK imported, you can now use its functionality within your component to interact with AWS services, such as uploading files to an S3 bucket.

