// Headshot.jsx

import './Headshot.scss';

export default function Headshot() {
  return (
    <div className="headshot">
      <div className="content">
        <h1>Photorealistic Generated Headshots</h1>

        <p>
          Tired of spending countless hours filling out job applications? 
          Pineapply will revolutionize your job search experience. With our 
          advanced technology, you can now automate the process of completing 
          job applications, saving you valuable time and effort.
        </p>

        <p>
          Simply provide your personal information, work history, and 
          qualifications, with our automated job application filler.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```

```scss
// Headshot.scss

.headshot {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2rem;

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      text-align: center;

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 60ch;

      &:not(:last-child) {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  }
}
```

The key changes:

- Flexbox for content container 
- rem units for fluid typography
- Media queries to modify styles responsively
- Limiting paragraph widths 
- Adding margins between paragraphs

